OL,7,FThe devastating diagnoses kept coming:
OL,8,Fhepatitis B the same year, hepatitis C
OL,9,Fseven years later, and eventually
OL,10,Faids. Reflecting on his ordeal, Neil
OL,11,Fshared, "I was very scared - a total,
OL,12,Femotional wreck. I didn't want to be
OL,13,Fhere. I didn't want to be a burden to
OL,14,Fmy family - why me?"
OL,16,FNeil's wife, Tina, echoes his
OL,17,Ffrustration: "I don't understand all
OL,18,Fthe delay, delay. You know justice
OL,19,Fdelayed is justice denied."
