OL,7,FRos Cooper, another affected
OL,8,Findividual, emphasises the need for
OL,9,Fthe government to acknowledge their
OL,10,Ffailings.
OL,12,FDespite interim payouts of #100,000 to
OL,13,Fabout 4,000 victims and bereaved
OL,14,Fpartners, she argues it's not enough.
