OL,7,FShe tells ITV News Central: "What we
OL,8,Fneed is for the state to actually
OL,9,Faccept, recognise and acknowledge what
OL,10,Fdid go wrong rather than saying 'we
OL,11,Fdid the best at the time and because
OL,12,Fwe think morally we should do
OL,13,Fsomething, we'll do something'.
OL,15,F"It is actually about saying, 'We got
OL,16,Fthis monumentally wrong, the fact that
OL,17,Fthis is the worst treatment disaster
OL,18,Fin the NHS and actually it's down to
OL,19,Fwhat we did, what previous
OL,20,Fadministrations did.'
