OL,7,F"That needs to be admitted and
OL,8,Facknowledged, people need to stand up
OL,9,Fand say, from the heart how sorry they
OL,10,Fare about that."
OL,12,FRos is adamant that Sir Brian
OL,13,FLangstaff's recommendations to widen
OL,14,Fthe compensation scheme to include
OL,15,Forphaned children and bereaved parents
OL,16,Fmust be actioned.
OL,18,FUntil everyone is treated fairly, she
OL,19,Ffeels unable to move on.
