OL,7,FAt 50, she longs to discover her
OL,8,Fidentity beyond the fight for justice.
OL,9,FHer mother poignantly reflects, "I
OL,10,Fthink of all the things I could have
OL,11,Fbeen doing, and Ros could have been
OL,12,Fdoing, but I've spent all the time
OL,13,Fdoing all this other stuff."
OL,15,FAndy, another voice in this chorus for
OL,16,Fjustice, hopes the report will lead to
OL,17,Fswift government action.
