OL,7,FHe said: "I hope the report comes out
OL,8,Fwith everything that we want. And I
OL,9,Fhope the government acts swiftly to
OL,10,Fcompensate people with, you know, as
OL,11,Fmuch as would give them a comfortable
OL,12,Flife for the rest of their lives. I
OL,13,Fdon't think that's too much to ask."
OL,15,FThe sentiment is shared by Colette,
OL,16,Fwho insists that more than apologies
OL,17,Fare needed - specific acknowledgment
OL,18,Fof the wrongs and a commitment to real
OL,19,Fchange.
